headline.main: Queen Elizabeth Marks St David's Day With Leek Gifts
headline.print_headline: Queen Elizabeth Marks St David's Day With Leek Gifts

lead_paragraph: European Union foreign ministers are to discuss whether to hold high-level talks with Israel soon amid concern over its settlement policy and commitment to a two-state solution, diplomats said Friday.
